### Search products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=1&pageSize=10&search=tubo&source=
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Create temporary local product
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/local-temp
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Temporary flange 4 in class 150",
  "unit": "PZA",
  "currency": "USD",
  "averageCost": 12.5,
  "lastCost": 12.5,
  "stock": 0,
  "branchCode": "02"
}

### Batch create temporary local products from extracted items
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/local-temp/batch-from-items
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "defaultCurrency": "USD",
  "items": [
